  "3123120": {
    "name": "杀死砖男",
    "steam_appid": 3123120,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >欢迎来到《Kill the Brickman》，这是一款回合制肉鸽打砖块游戏，深受复古街机热潮启发。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过组合圣物、弹夹布局以及能够爆炸、腐蚀和成倍增加的奇异子弹，打造你自己的爆弹配装。每场游戏都是全新的实验。每次构建都是烧脑的谜题。每颗子弹都是炸开砖块、花光钱财的工具。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一路闯关射击，直面强大首领，并探索协同效应，将你的卑微小枪打造成足以征服星系的手炮。游戏的深度远不止瞄准射击那么简单，更有数百件圣物和丰富的构建选择等你探索。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>主任务</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123120/extras/e7e7abf08a4dad326ecc93a888c48c33.poster.avif?t=1758614631\" width=600 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123120/extras/e7e7abf08a4dad326ecc93a888c48c33.webm?t=1758614631\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123120/extras/e7e7abf08a4dad326ecc93a888c48c33.mp4?t=1758614631\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >选择章节和武器，有种的话还能从星际赏金榜上领取额外任务，用枪林弹雨射出一条胜利之路。然而，获胜并非易事，所以务必合理构建和堆叠，才能带着钞票满载而归。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>配装</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123120/extras/c80927a70f52d58bd9363338fab7fb8c.poster.avif?t=1758614631\" width=600 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123120/extras/c80927a70f52d58bd9363338fab7fb8c.webm?t=1758614631\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123120/extras/c80927a70f52d58bd9363338fab7fb8c.mp4?t=1758614631\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >选择你的枪械，它们各有各的初始技能。留意商店中的弹夹，它们甚至能赋予你的子弹更多技能；没错，它们也拥有技能。这只是技能加技能而已。打造你的构建，使用圣物加强战力；没错，它们同样拥有技能。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>地点</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123120/extras/1a7216c70ebde7709733714715087cc7.poster.avif?t=1758614631\" width=600 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123120/extras/1a7216c70ebde7709733714715087cc7.webm?t=1758614631\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123120/extras/1a7216c70ebde7709733714715087cc7.mp4?t=1758614631\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >选择章节，拣选随身武器，有种的话还能从星际赏金榜上领取额外任务，用枪林弹雨射出一条胜利之路。然而，获胜并非易事，所以务必合理构建和堆叠，才能带着钞票满载而归。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>“殚”精要诀（看懂这个笑话了吗？？？）</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >如果你自认为能顶住压力，那就接受额外的任务吧。丰厚的奖励正静候勇者的到来。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >记得在商店挥霍钱财。要是不合你的需求，就再抽一把！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >当设施出现时，务必要盯紧了，它们说不定会助你一臂之力。</p></li></ul>",
